highlights.description: Predictive diagnostics facilitates vehicle-specific prediction of the component and system health, along with optimized planning of maintenance tasks based on data from the connected vehicle. ​This solution is built without usage of any third party sensor and provide recommendations for effective usage of Battery , filters , engine  and transmission components​ with improved lifetime.

Real time information on the conditions leadings to the collision incidents. Post an accident, reporting of upto3 levels of severity with accident detailing backend report with trajectory of vehicle, speed, angle of impact and location maps.

Get the overall performance of your fleet in a single window categorized into various parameters like most running time, idling time, cumulative distance travelled, various penalties and ratios. Based on this view, best and worst performing fleet can be recognized.

: A comprehensive view of fuel usage in the vehicle. Driver behavior based fuel economy monitoring (Driver idling, AC On while idle, HA, HB, Coasting)​ with suggestions on improving the driver behavior for better fuel economy.
